# GitHub Repositories Viewer

This project provides a user-friendly interface to view GitHub repositories for a specified user. You can adjust the number of repositories displayed per page and easily navigate through the pages. The application offers both list-based pagination and button-based pagination for your convenience.

## Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/github-repositories-viewer.git
cd github-repositories-viewer
